    Cherry blossoms on the Shirokawa River in Gion.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
    祇園の白川に咲くしだれ桜。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Kyoto" /><category term="Cherry Blossoms" /><summary type="html">Cherry blossoms on the Shirokawa River in Gion.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2203_A7R06017.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2203_A7R06017.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Horin-ji Pagoda・法輪寺の塔</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220322/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Horin-ji Pagoda・法輪寺の塔" /><published>2022-03-22T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2022-03-22T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/horinji</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220322/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
    The pagoda at Horin-ji temple, framed by cherry blossoms.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
    桜の花に縁取られた法輪寺の塔。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Arashiyama" /><category term="Temples" /><category term="Cherry Blossoms" /><summary type="html">The pagoda at Horin-ji temple, framed by cherry blossoms.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2203_A7R05904.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2203_A7R05904.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Camellia Water Basin・手水鉢の椿</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220320/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Camellia Water Basin・手水鉢の椿" /><published>2022-03-20T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2022-03-20T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/nisonin</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220320/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
    Camellias arranged in the water basin &lt;em&gt;(chōzubachi) &lt;/em&gt; at Nison-in Temple.
&lt;/p&gt;

