    二尊院の手水鉢中に置かれた椿。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Arashiyama" /><category term="Temples" /><category term="Flowers" /><summary type="html">Camellias arranged in the water basin (chōzubachi) at Nison-in Temple.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2203_A7R05886.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2203_A7R05886.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Kurumazaki Jinja・車折神社</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220319/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Kurumazaki Jinja・車折神社" /><published>2022-03-19T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2022-03-19T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/kurumazaki</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220319/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
    A small shrine at Kurumazaki Jinja with a nice cherry tree.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
    車折神社の小さな神社に、素敵な桜の木が。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Kyoto" /><category term="Shrines" /><category term="Cherry Blossoms" /><summary type="html">A small shrine at Kurumazaki Jinja with a nice cherry tree.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2203_A7R05860.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2203_A7R05860.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Shinsenen・神泉苑</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220318/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Shinsenen・神泉苑" /><published>2022-03-18T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2022-03-18T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/duck</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220318/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
    One of the ducks in the pond at Shinsenen, said to be the oldest existing garden in Kyoto. It was created in 794 as the emperor&apos;s private garden, part of the original palace from the time of Heian-Kyo.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
    京都に現存する最古の庭園といわれる神泉苑の池にいる鴨の一羽。794年に天皇の私的な庭園として造られたもので、平安京の時代からある宮殿の一部であった。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Kyoto" /><category term="Temples" /><category term="Gardens" /><summary type="html">One of the ducks in the pond at Shinsenen, said to be the oldest existing garden in Kyoto. It was created in 794 as the emperor&apos;s private garden, part of the original palace from the time of Heian-Kyo.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2203_IMG_5084.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2203_IMG_5084.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Peach Blossoms・桃の花</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220317/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Peach Blossoms・桃の花" /><published>2022-03-17T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2022-03-17T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/peacj</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220317/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
    Peach blossoms on the steps of Horin-ji Temple.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
    法輪寺の階段に咲く桃の花。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Arashiyama" /><category term="Flowers" /><summary type="html">Peach blossoms on the steps of Horin-ji Temple.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2203_A7R05850.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2203_A7R05850.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Camellia</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220316/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Camellia" /><published>2022-03-16T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2022-03-16T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/camelia</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220316/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
